Installation¶

Install $project by running:

git clone https://github.com/keatonrohlfs/QUAD

Usage¶

Start $project by running:

docker compose build && docker compose start

Stop $project by running:

docker compose down

Stop $project and clear the databases by running:

docker compose down -v
